                            <div id="answer-1" class="block-question second-answer" >
                                <div class="container-question">
                                    <h3 id="popular-answer">Popular Answer</h3>
                                    <div >
                                        <p>I'd guess it's because a lot of programmers are familiar with Java and Java, for all its faults as a language, has excellent library and tool support.  Also, the layer of VM indirection prevents the apps from being too tightly coupled to the hardware. </p>

